Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.06,0:01:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.90,0:01:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.76,0:01:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.96,0:01:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要…回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.15,0:01:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  竟然讓那種下等妖怪乘虛而入
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.47,0:01:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這若是稍有差池怕會危及到生命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.52,0:01:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我振作些  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.25,0:01:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.15,0:01:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能聽到老師的聲音  得回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.02,0:02:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  是去哪個家？ 在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.22,0:02:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到處晃悠著做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.97,0:02:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目該不會是迷路了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是寄住在三世子家的那個孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是還沒能記住回家的路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦子真不好使
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.13,0:02:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰讓這太恐怖了我不敢過去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.49,0:02:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是我想去哪都是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.91,0:02:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要住下去…我也想要住下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往回走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.67,0:02:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要再去學校一次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.58,0:02:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家真的都看不到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有這麼多恐怖的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神社？ 竟然會在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好  如果被妖怪追趕的話就逃到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  就把這裡當作秘密基地好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.80,0:03:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有誰來打攪  安靜的…只屬於我的地方

Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:37.69,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1.6\shad2\bord1}遙遙家路

Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.83,0:03:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.14,0:03:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  三世子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.89,0:03:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還剩下這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.82,0:03:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.76,0:03:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.03,0:03:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是不想吃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.21,0:03:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  三世子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.98,0:04:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  三世子  要和貴志君一起去學校喲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經和菜緒醬約好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴志君  別太在意了  要多吃些哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.96,0:04:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想什麼時候能吃一次看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.14,0:04:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個不是夏目嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.62,0:04:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  是三世子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.12,0:04:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  三世子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.16,0:04:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你和夏目同居呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真害臊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真害臊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  給我住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.34,0:05:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真害臊  真害臊  真害臊  真害臊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三世子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.88,0:05:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.89,0:05:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得去道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.35,0:05:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不是她的錯  都怪我…來到了這個家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.09,0:05:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又留下這麼多！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.26,0:05:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三世子  怎麼了？ 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三世子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三世子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  為什麼那個孩子會來我們家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.44,0:06:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三世子  睡覺前爸爸給你講好多好多的故事好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你呢  明天就要和貴志君一起去學校喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三世子她在撒嬌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.97,0:06:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚就睡在我的房間裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴志君你一個人不怕吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.54,0:06:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就晚安了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就看一眼沒關係吧？ 就只是今天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.94,0:07:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不行  不能再翻看了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.99,0:07:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要開始疼痛了  不能再看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.09,0:07:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  我不寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.41,0:07:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  雖然已不再身邊  但一定為我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.60,0:07:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.28,0:07:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走得離我更遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.37,0:07:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你的家在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.22,0:07:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真正的家呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是真正的家？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就是你父母所住的家　
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不記得嗎？ 你的爸爸和媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不記得我媽媽了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.57,0:08:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.43,0:08:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.36,0:08:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是非常地非常的溫柔！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定曾是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明說是不記得但怎麼又說得出口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.76,0:08:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那種口氣算什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的爸爸才是最溫柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的家？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪  明明說是不記得…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.64,0:08:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果回到真正的家裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會能想起更多爸爸的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想起很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.09,0:09:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而化為更多的傷痛的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的家？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.02,0:09:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  夏目夫婦的家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.67,0:09:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像從館花先生那收到過家庭住址
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.24,0:09:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過要這做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…想要作為護身符
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.83,0:09:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.68,0:09:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離這裡不遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說城町的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.67,0:09:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是沿著城川河徑直向西走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.08,0:09:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  又有小妖怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.96,0:09:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我替你吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.68,0:09:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小姑娘又剩飯了  真不是個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.42,0:10:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我替你吃掉好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢  絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.48,0:10:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去一邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.87,0:10:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好凶  好凶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.15,0:10:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走遠點  走更遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.77,0:10:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以給別人添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城町  是沿著城川河向西直走

Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.79,0:11:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦  現在幾點了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.37,0:11:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得趕緊回去了  不然又給別人添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.24,0:11:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  只是打雷而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.09,0:11:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得趕緊回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.87,0:11:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快！ 趕快！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.21,0:12:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驚擾大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能找到真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可憐  看來是嚇壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴志君  你先進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要去向大家道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.40,0:12:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和三世子先吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.42,0:12:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.09,0:12:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.21,0:12:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我爸爸媽媽非得去道歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我爸爸媽媽要被指責呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是你有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.61,0:12:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我離開這
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙給我遠離這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.58,0:13:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我離開…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城町…沿著城川河…徑直向西…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡有我的家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.92,0:13:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家吧  回家吧…我真正的家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.90,0:13:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已成虛無的家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…爸爸…爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實已是無數次…無數次地呼喚過了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而果然仍舊無人會應答
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是如何的呼喚  企盼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會有遙不可及的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果那以後還是未能夠抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷失方向  精疲力竭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.26,0:14:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是決意放棄無法給與答覆的呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.37,0:14:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲傷的想要忘卻的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我替你吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我畫張嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.24,0:14:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  即便如此  那也是拼湊出現在的我的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是何等的傷痛  那也是我最重要的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.45,0:14:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記憶也好  內心也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.62,0:14:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都讓我吃掉好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.63,0:14:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.99,0:14:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.89,0:14:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.23,0:14:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴志君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.97,0:14:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔子阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:14:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路小心  貴志君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  我要…回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.48,0:15:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  把它妖力打散了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.78,0:15:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不過是區區蟲子一般
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.93,0:15:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在呼喚我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了我的記憶嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你的記憶沒有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.55,0:16:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正不過是在得到友人帳之前的交往而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.20,0:16:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城町  沿著城川河徑直向西走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.70,0:17:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我畫的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是個亂來的小孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.29,0:17:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明畫在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:17:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸還沒擦掉反而替我留下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.08,0:18:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.27,0:18:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有稍微想起些在這裡的生活呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然基本上都記不起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多…很多的重要的回憶…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都被我忘得一乾二淨了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.43,0:18:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  這個院子裡的某處有媽媽種下的花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.56,0:18:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經完全分辨不出了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴志
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.43,0:18:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴志  今年要是也開花就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.18,0:18:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠一直地一直地開花就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.94,0:19:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴志
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.63,0:19:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.11,0:19:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了  我的家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後  身體相當地疲乏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.68,0:19:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一味的趕路回家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒能吃上那家的烏冬面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得的是老師竟然沒有發脾氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.77,0:19:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:19:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來  貴志
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.19,0:20:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.21,0:20:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了  這次又是哪邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該就在附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.66,0:20:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這已經是第三次了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.72,0:20:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.72,0:20:21.47,small,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波子汽水  波子汽水…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.70,0:20:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目大人  先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.54,0:20:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先告辭  先告辭！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波子汽水  波子汽水…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…第六感覺應該是這邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.15,0:20:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.00,0:20:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.93,0:20:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.61,0:20:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笹田
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.31,0:20:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多軌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們終於來了  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  被你們捷足先登
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.37,0:20:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是詳細調查過的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.45,0:20:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽夏目說你們今天會來就在這等著了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說有波子汽水湧出來的…就是這裡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.69,0:21:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼呢  不是通紅的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.59,0:21:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的咯  生銹了唄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.52,0:21:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  只要運氣不太壞  不會弄壞肚子的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.20,0:21:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  西村  你就先喝喝看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.03,0:21:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭剪刀布來決定！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.97,0:21:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有過悲傷  有過難過的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.23,0:21:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這今後的日子裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.00,0:21:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許還會再有那樣的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.24,0:21:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.62,0:21:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  準備好了  要照了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.20,0:21:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  貴志  再靠近點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  笑笑  貴志君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.16,0:21:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看  有沒有拍進去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.66,0:21:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.79,0:22:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚是…炸牛肉餅的藍調
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.55,0:22:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滋叔叔  塔子阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.00,0:22:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…能夠再照一張嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.88,0:22:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓五郎  要老實待著喲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.06,0:22:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法忘卻的…寶貴的日子

